{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"427f6601-59cf-4232-a7be-3761243c0bfd","content":"There are two reliable, programmatic approaches — both pull the info straight from your installed SDK rather than relying on docs:\n\n### 1. Inspect the workload manifest JSON\n\n```bash\n# Find your SDK path\nSDK_PATH=$(dotnet --list-sdks | tail -1 | awk '{print $2}' | tr -d '[]')\n\n# Find the Android workload manifest\nfind \"$SDK_PATH/../sdk-manifests\" -path '*/microsoft.net.sdk.android/WorkloadManifest.json' \\\n  | xargs cat | python3 -m json.tool\n```\n\nThis JSON lists every pack (and its exact version) the MAUI Android workload requires.\n\n### 2. Read the resolved Android SDK props from an installed pack\n\nAfter running `dotnet workload install maui-android`:\n\n```bash\n# The installed pack's targets/props define the exact requirements\nfind \"$(dotnet --list-sdks | tail -1 | awk '{print $2}' | tr -d '[]')/../packs/Microsoft.Android.Sdk\"* \\\n  -name '*.props' -o -name '*.targets' \\\n  | xargs grep -hE 'AndroidSdkBuildToolsVersion|compileSdkVersion|AndroidLatestStableApiLevel|CommandLineToolsVersion'\n```\n\nThis gives you MSBuild properties like:\n\n| Property | What it controls |\n|---|---|\n| `AndroidSdkBuildToolsVersion` | `build-tools;XX.Y.Z` |\n| `AndroidLatestStableApiLevel` | `platforms;android-XX` |\n| `CommandLineToolsVersion` | `cmdline-tools;XX.0` |\n\n### Putting it together in CI\n\n```bash\n# Resolve the values, then install exactly what's needed\nBT=$(grep -r 'AndroidSdkBuildToolsVersion' \"$PACKS_DIR\" | grep -oP '>\\K[^<]+')\nAPI=$(grep -r 'AndroidLatestStableApiLevel' \"$PACKS_DIR\" | grep -oP '>\\K[^<]+')\nCLT=$(grep -r 'CommandLineToolsVersion' \"$PACKS_DIR\" | grep -oP '>\\K[^<]+')\n\nsdkmanager \"build-tools;${BT}\" \"platforms;android-${API}\" \"cmdline-tools;${CLT}\"\n```\n\nThis way your CI always installs exactly what your SDK version expects — no hardcoded versions to maintain.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"a50ebe38-5fe3-4202-8320-48ff75a06859","outputTokens":591,"requestId":"1100:FD35D:1742B6E:1A77719:69FE878E"},"id":"a3a52b29-4fd8-45da-89bc-0e6e00490deb","timestamp":"2026-05-09T01:02:18.503Z","parentId":"077f9b77-f2a4-4d9b-aba8-575794e339f6"}
